Base Image Update
1          Subscription Management Repository Update – This will enable all file types
a.              Open a Terminal Window

b.              sudo subscription-manager repos --enable codeready-builder-for-rhel-8-$(arch)-rpms

c.         sudo dnf install https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-8.noarch.rpm

d.              Install 1 Package – Total Size 22 k – Installed Size 32 k – Is this OK [y/N] – y

·                Installed: epel-release-8-14.el8.noarch

·                Complete

e.              sudo yum install ntfs-3g

f.               Install 2 Packages – Total Size 318 k – Installed Size 685 k – Is this OK [y/N] – y

g.              Extra Packages for Enterprise Linux 8 -  Is this OK [y/N] - y

·                Installed: ntfs-3g-2:2021.8.22-2.el8.x86_64

·                Complete

